{"repo": "google/tunix", "pull_number": 1151, "instance_id": "google__tunix-1151", "issue_numbers": [1149], "base_commit": "b12123542511e45814ec3ff798ec4fb30b0b48e8", "patch": "diff --git a/tunix/generate/sglang_jax_sampler.py b/tunix/generate/sglang_jax_sampler.py\nindex 7d61c6201..a4d5b0895 100644\n--- a/tunix/generate/sglang_jax_sampler.py\n+++ b/tunix/generate/sglang_jax_sampler.py\n@@ -14,6 +14,8 @@\n \n \"\"\"Sampler for sglang-jax-style autoregressive decoding using JAX and NNX models.\"\"\"\n \n+import asyncio\n+import concurrent\n import dataclasses\n import math\n from typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional, Tuple, Union\n@@ -21,7 +23,6 @@\n from absl import logging\n from flax import nnx\n import jax\n-import jax.numpy as jnp\n import jaxtyping\n import numpy as np\n from sgl_jax.srt.entrypoints.engine import Engine\n@@ -315,7 +316,8 @@ def __call__(\n         logging.log_first_n(\n             logging.INFO,\n             f\"Failed to update sampling_params with kwargs: {kwargs}.\"\n-            f\" Error: {e}\", 1\n+            f\" Error: {e}\",\n+            1,\n         )\n \n     sampling_params = [\n@@ -380,23 +382,23 @@ def _generate_with_loop_guard(\n     loop = get_or_create_event_loop()\n \n     if not loop.is_running():\n-      res = loop.run_until_complete(coro)\n-      return res\n-\n-    import concurrent\n+      try:\n+        return loop.run_until_complete(coro)\n+      finally:\n+        loop.close()\n \n     def wrap_generate():\n       loop = get_or_create_event_loop()\n-      return loop.run_until_complete(coro)\n+      try:\n+        return loop.run_until_complete(coro)\n+      finally:\n+        loop.close()\n \n     with concurrent.futures.ThreadPoolExecutor() as executor:\n       future = executor.submit(wrap_generate)\n       return future.result()\n \n \n-import asyncio\n-\n-\n def get_or_create_event_loop():\n   try:\n     loop = asyncio.get_running_loop()\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "[BUG] CPU OOM with sglangjax as rollout when training 50steps\n**Expected Behavior**\n\nTrain until the max steps.\n\n**Actual Behavior**\n\nFail to train due to CPU OOM.\n\n```bash\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.214982970Z [severity: ERROR] Scheduler hit an exception: Traceback (most recent call last):\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215014026Z [severity: ERROR] File \"/opt/venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/sgl_jax/srt/managers/scheduler.py\", line 1609, in scheduler_loop_after_create\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215017759Z [severity: ERROR] scheduler.event_loop_overlap()\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215020178Z [severity: ERROR] File \"/opt/venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/sgl_jax/srt/managers/scheduler.py\", line 569, in event_loop_overlap\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215022451Z [severity: ERROR] result = self.run_batch(batch)\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215024780Z [severity: ERROR] ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215027730Z [severity: ERROR] File \"/opt/venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/sgl_jax/srt/managers/scheduler.py\", line 1315, in run_batch\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215050533Z [severity: ERROR] model_worker_batch = batch.get_model_worker_batch(\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215052472Z [severity: ERROR] ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215054432Z [severity: ERROR] File \"/opt/venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/sgl_jax/srt/managers/schedule_batch.py\", line 1299, in get_model_worker_batch\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215056584Z [severity: ERROR] cache_loc_cpu = np.empty(total_cache_loc_size, dtype=np.int32)\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215058276Z [severity: ERROR] ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\nERROR 2026-02-17T10:53:50.215059866Z [severity: ERROR] numpy._core._exceptions._ArrayMemoryError: Unable to allocate 16.0 MiB for an array with shape (4194304,) and data type int32\n\n```\n\n**Steps to Reproduce the Problem**\n\n@lc5211  reports this problem in Pathways. But I can also reproduce the abnormal memory usage not in Pathways.  Run `ROLLOUT_ENGINE=sglang_jax python3 examples/deepscaler/train_deepscaler_nb.py`.\n\n<!---\nIf possible, provide a link to a [Colab Notebook](https://research.google.com/colaboratory/),\nwhich reproduces the bug.\n-->\n\n**Environment**\n\n- **OS:** tpu-v5p-8\n- **Project Version:** [e.g., 0.0.1]\n\n```bash\nflax                         0.12.4\njax                          0.8.1\njaxlib                       0.8.1\njaxtyping                    0.3.9\nlibtpu                       0.0.30\nsglang-jax                   main-6a61469da565d42cf38eb6105a040853a3afffdf\ntunix                     linchai_deepscaler:dd36d06bf769512b0fe0205b542a12e61ba0b6cd\n```\n\n**Checklist**\n\n- [ ] I have searched the existing issues for a similar bug report.\n- [ ] I have provided all the required information in the \"Environment\" section.\n- [ ] I have provided a minimal, reproducible example.\n\n**Would you like to help us fix it?**\nYes.\n\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/google/tunix/commit/1fd21041bde732a21c51217c07a0b1587bd77a8d"], "created_at": "2026-02-25T06:23:52Z"}
